title: Did Stuart Minkus Become Chanel West Coast?
subtitle: Lee Norris, better known as Cory Matthews' nerdy middle school classmate Stuart Minkus on 'Boy Meets World,' did not become actress Chanel West Coast.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The actor who played Stuart Minkus on the television series Boy Meets World become the actress Chanel West Coast.
